messages.content: Vega was playing on the playground she had in her mindscape. She was having so much fun! It was nice and comfortable in here to her
However, There was one thing she was ignoring.
A dark shadow watching her from behind the tree. It was shaped like a kind of parent figure. The manifestation of Vegas fears, nightmares, and cracks
( @Iris  feel free to yeet Akousa in now that they both snzz)
Akosua found herself here. "This must be a dream."

Vega was playing on the playground still when she fell. "Owie....."

This caused the "parent figure" to start yelling at Vega
"Hey!" Akosua stood between the two

Vega was curled up into a ball, shaking a bit. When she heard Akosuas voice she looked up. "Big sis Sua.....?"

The "Parent Figure" just ignored Akosua and kept yelling nonsensical stuff at Vega
"Leave her alone!"
They only yelled more causing Vegas back to glow a bit as the young mun kept crying
Akosua breathed in through her nose
She dislocated her arm to do a hamon extendo arm thing

It blasted the figure away, for now.

Vegas back is still glowing, perhaps Akousa should look
Akosua looked at her back
She could see the scars and cracks the small mun had....
"Oh no..."
she was pissed
not to the point where she'd say the fuck word, but close
She hugged Vega
She sniffled and hugged back
"I'm here...I'll keep you safe."
"H-how did yo-you even come here big sis Sua....?"
"I don't know. I think this is a dream."
"Th-this is where I go when I sleep..."
"It's like your dream world!"
She nodded a bit
"It looks like a fun playground!"
"Thanks!!!!! I like playgrounds..."
"Do you wanna play?"
She nodded happily
"What do you want to play?"
"Uhhh..." she hummed a bit
Akosua hummed too.
She hummed a song she always really liked
It was dancing queen by abba
Vega tried to hum along
Akosua noticed. "Do you know this song, Vega?"
"No but it sounds nice!!!"
"It's called dancing queen and it's one of my favorite songs!"
"Oooo...."
"I could play it when I wake up!"
She nodded "Yes please!!!!"
"It's a very good song! What songs do you like?"
"I like the wheels on the bus!!!!!!" She hummed the song
Akosua new the song and hummed along with her
"Here's one I saw on tv! A B C D E F G, how I wonder what you are- wait, I think I got that wrong."
She blinked, staring wide eyed as she slowly figured it out.
"Wait....they're the SAME SONG!"
Vegas now :O
"OH MY GOD!"
"HOLY CRAP, IT WAS LIKE THIS ALL ALONG?!"
"No bad words!!!"
"Crap isn't a bad word..."
"It's not. I've heard all the bad words!"

"No saying that word!!"

The figure was coming back
Akosua noticed and held Vega close
She held onto her tightly, sniffling a bit "No bad words...."
"Vega? are you ok?"

"I don't like those bad words...."

The figure was yelling again, this time you could understand it. It was saying alot of nasty words with crap thrown in as one. This is what Vega had heard almost daily...
Akosua didn't want to get the clackers. *This is a dream world, right? Can I make anything?*
//can she create anything?
(She can)
She creates a glowing blue spear and throws it at the figure
It works!
Akosua just holds Vega
"the thing is gone now."
She looked up at her "Th-thanks big sis sua...." she smiled
"no problem, Vega." She sets Vega down on the ground
She pulled the other to the playground "Play!!!"
"What do you want to play?"
She ran over to the monkey bars and tried to grab onto them "Look!!!!!!"
@Iris
"I've never seen these before."
"Monkey bars!!! I can show you how to use them!!!" She smiled
"Show me!"
She showed her how to use them!
"I thought they work like this." She hopped on top of the monkey bars and began crawling
She giggled "No silly!!!"
She tried it the normal way. "this is fun!"
"I know!!!!!! I like them.." She hummed
"I see why!"
Vega hopped off "I think im gonna wake up....."
"ok I'll join you."
And just like that, they where gone from the mindscape
Vega was back here and just siting and drawing! She was trying to ignore the "parent figure" staring at her
Shes scared....the "parent figure" is yelling again
Akosua showed up here by hugging her.
She threw a bone at the figure
After that Vega had snapped back to reality
Shes back here and waiting for Opal to show up
after a bit, Opal showed up "Vega ?"
She ran over quickly the figure once again yelling "T-Thats it...." she whimpered and pointed
Opal hugged vega close and looked directly at the figure "Vega, it's ok, they aren't *real*, remember that."
"I-Its scary...." She sniffled "I-I dont like the yelling....
She kept keeping Vega close "Hey, it's ok, I'm here, stay close to me"

She nodded and stayed in the hug "O-Ok mama...."

The second the figure heard that it tired to attack Opal
Opal put her arms up to defend herself, and pushing it back
//should I bring in Akosua?
(Yeye. Having any of her fam here helps
Akosua manifested a sword "STAY AWAY FROM OUR MOM!"
"Akosua !" Opal sighed out od relief, "I'm glad you're here too!"
Akosua fights the figure

Vega watches them, slowly gaining courage. 

It kept trying to fight them
Opal manifested boomerangs, filled with hamon, to fight the figure
It kept trying to yell at Vega all while trying to dodge
She manifested a scarf and warped it around the figure's mouth to try to silence it
It seemed to help a little. It definitely helped Vega calm down
Akosua stabbed the silhouette

That really didnt do much. It was more of a shadow then anything....

Vega took a step forward and mumbled something
Opal stayed closed to her, but still behind "Come on sweetie, say it louder!"

She took a deep breath to calm herself "Leave my mama and big sis Sua alone....."

The figure started to try and yell again
Opal tighten the scarf around the figure's mouth "you're doing great Vega !"

She was scared but needed to do this. "I said......LEAVE MY MAMA AND BIG SIS SUA ALONE YOU _**ASSHOLE**_!" She screamed

The figure screeched and exploded into light
Opal clapped and hugged Vega "you did it !"
She hugged back giggling happily
Akosua was surprised
She joined the hug tho
"My back doesn't hurt anymore!!!!!" She smiled
"that's great!"
@Radioactive Lain
Opal smiled warmly "That's good to hear !"
"Thank you for helping me mama and big sis Sua....." She smiled
"Hey, it's what a family is for, afterall!"
She smiled happily, tail wagging
Sua is happy
"Now you'll be at peace in your own mind, sweetheart!"
She smiled more "Yay!!!!!!"
Akosua was bouncy
"Lets play on the playground together!!!!"
"I'll watch you two!" Opal sat down
Akosua runs to the playground and trips
Vega plays on the monkey bars!!!!! There doesnt seem to be shadows.....anywhere.....no one has a shadow in her mindscape...
Opal thought it was weird, but decided to ignore it, mindscapes are weird afterall
"Mama!!!! Look at me!!!" She giggled
Opal clapped "Great Vega !"
Akosua was climbing up a slide
Vegas having tons of fun
